@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Claim Daily Bonus
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/me/daily-bonus
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Certificates
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shop/certificates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buy Certificate
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shop/certificates/CERTIFICATE_ID_HERE/buy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Certificates
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/certificates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
